{"title":"JavaScript async (非同步) , sync (同步)","uid":"c2201de0d6e77cfe16bec9bb05e5b3de","slug":"async (非同步) , sync (同步)","date":"2020-12-09T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-06-13T13:59:22.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/async (非同步) , sync (同步).json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<p>上篇<a href=\"https://hackmd.io/2q-URsBTTOS3doStyuSTbw\">Promise</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"生活範例：\"><a href=\"#生活範例：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"生活範例：\"></a>生活範例：</h2><ul>\n<li>async(非同步) :</li>\n</ul>\n<ol>\n<li>去醫院掛號</li>\n<li>等護士叫，可以先去上廁所</li>\n<li>護士叫了，我在過去</li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li>sync(同步) :</li>\n</ul>\n<ol>\n<li>去醫院掛號</li>\n<li>在櫃檯等，等到護士說好了</li>\n<li>我才能去上廁所</li>\n</ol>\n<h1 id=\"實作解析：\"><a href=\"#實作解析：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"實作解析：\"></a>實作解析：</h1><p><a href=\"https://codesandbox.io/s/hw2-function-mouxianwang-6904-zuoyejiexiforked-j70zb?file=/src/index.js\">撈取資料實作範例</a><br>另一個 Js 檔案(utils.js 是資料庫)</p>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"try-catch-捕捉錯誤\"><a href=\"#try-catch-捕捉錯誤\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"try()catch() 捕捉錯誤\"></a>try()catch() 捕捉錯誤</h3><p>語法：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">try (用鑰匙開門)&#123;\n\n  小妹用自己鑰匙開自己房門成功\n  \n&#125; catch()&#123;\n\n  小妹用哥哥鑰匙開自己房門失敗\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">&#x2F;&#x2F; foo 透過 async 回傳會得到一個 foo()\n&#x2F;&#x2F; foo() 是一個 promise\n\nconst foo &#x3D; async()&#x3D;&gt;&#123;\n    return &#123;\n    a:1,\n    b:2\n    &#125;\n&#125;\n\n&#x2F;&#x2F; 1. promise 版本\n\nfoo().then((data)&#x3D;&gt;&#123;\n    \n&#125;).catch(error&#x3D;&gt;&#123;\n\n&#125;)\n\n\n\n&#x2F;&#x2F; 2. async 版本\n\nasync()&#x3D;&gt;&#123;\n    try &#123;\n        const data2 &#x3D; await foo ()\n    &#125;catch(error)&#123;\n        return(error)\n    &#125;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n\n\n\n\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"小叮嚀：\"><a href=\"#小叮嚀：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"小叮嚀：\"></a>小叮嚀：</h3><ol>\n<li><p><strong>.then().catch()是Promise的用法，<br>async 沒有 .then().catch()，<br>所以只好用 try() catch() 來捕捉錯誤</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>await(等待)，外層一定要有 async(非同步)包裹著</strong></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n","text":"上篇Promise 生活範例： async(非同步) : 去醫院掛號 等護士叫，可以先去上廁所 護士叫了，我在過去 sync(同步) : 去醫院掛號 在櫃檯等，等到護士說好了 我才能去上廁所 實作解析：撈取資料實作範例另一個 Js 檔案(utils.js 是資料庫) try()c...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":829,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"JavaScript","slug":"JavaScript","count":45,"path":"api/categories/JavaScript.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"JavaScript","slug":"JavaScript","count":39,"path":"api/tags/JavaScript.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E7%AF%84%E4%BE%8B%EF%BC%9A\"><span class=\"toc-text\">生活範例：</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AF%A6%E4%BD%9C%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90%EF%BC%9A\"><span class=\"toc-text\">實作解析：</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#try-catch-%E6%8D%95%E6%8D%89%E9%8C%AF%E8%AA%A4\"><span class=\"toc-text\">try()catch() 捕捉錯誤</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%B0%8F%E5%8F%AE%E5%9A%80%EF%BC%9A\"><span class=\"toc-text\">小叮嚀：</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Michael","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"happy coding!","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Michael0520","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"JavaScript (Promise)(es6)","uid":"2329c3a140d479f71fd074e5ee1e2f1e","slug":"JS (Promise)(es6)","date":"2020-12-09T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-06-13T13:59:22.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/JS (Promise)(es6).json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"text":"下篇筆記 async(非同步),sync(同步) ES5&#x2F;